li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/queryCommandEnabled\"><code>queryCommandEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/queryCommandSupported\"><code>queryCommandSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/querySelector\"><code>querySelector()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/querySelectorAll\"><code>querySelectorAll()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>registerElement()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/releaseCapture\"><code>releaseCapture()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/replaceChildren\"><code>replaceChildren()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/requestStorageAccess\"><code>requestStorageAccess()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/write\"><code>write()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/writeln\"><code>writeln()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandar